  this film is the fourth of five collaborations between ferrell and mckay , following anchorman : the legend of ron burgundy ( 2004 ) , talladega nights : the ballad of ricky bobby ( 2006 ) , step brothers ( 2008 ) , and followed by anchorman 2 : the legend continues ( 2013 ) .

one fact among the false gossip : he invented the guitar ! he played defective allen gamble in " the other guys " ! he taught cowbell at usc !

